{"data":[{"date":"14:47 17/07","title":"L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00f3t hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n UAE v\u00e0 Palestine.</h2><h2>AFC mu\u1ed1n&nbsp;b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD 2018. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 g\u1ed3m Hong Kong, L\u00e0o v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0i Loan, trong khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i c\u00f9ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam nam chung bang voi Nhat Ban tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 UAE v\u00e0 Palestine</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y sau khi 2 qu\u1ed1c gia UAE v\u00e0 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i l\u00ean Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 - AFC v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u00f3m 4 khi ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i, tr\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf Indonesia \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n s\u1ebd b\u1ed1c th\u0103m b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 cho UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng Erick Thohir - Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch&nbsp;\u1ee6y ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ASIAD Indonesia chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;AFC mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu Palestine v\u00e0 UAE mu\u1ed1n tham d\u1ef1, ch\u1ec9 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. AFC r\u1ea5t d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t c\u1eadp&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1c t\u1eeb trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA)&nbsp;cho hay k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng v\u00ec sai s\u00f3t tr\u00ean m\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c chia b\u1ea3ng h\u00f4m 5/7 v\u1eeba qua ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp v\u1edbi OCA v\u00e0 AFC \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\">VFF c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1355","checkdouble":"191435"},{"date":"15:04 17/07","title":"Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/wenger-thua-nhan-sai-lam-khi-o-lai-arsenal-qua-lau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal t\u1edbi h\u01a1n 20 n\u0103m ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</h2><h2>Wenger sai l\u1ea7m khi \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/soc-arsene-wenger-cong-bo-quyet-dinh-tu-chuc-172-184670.html\" target=\"_blank\">Wenger \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Arsenal</span> sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal. Wenger kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f4ng C\u0110V Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 quay l\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u201cgi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Wenger \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u00f4ng n\u00ean r\u1eddi kh\u1edfi Arsenal s\u1edbm h\u01a1n. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 n\u00ean ch\u1ea7n ch\u1eeb trong vi\u1ec7c ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wenger \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wenger \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/wenger-thua-nhan-sai-lam-khi-o-lai-arsenal-qua-lau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean k\u00eanh RTL c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 68 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cC\u00f3 l\u1ebd sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong 22 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111i \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng th\u00edch nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t t\u00f9 nh\u00e2n khi c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t ra\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Wenger t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Wenger \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc hay sau th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a Domenech. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00ec th\u00edch v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y n\u00f3 th\u00fa v\u1ecb h\u01a1n vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i t\u1eebng \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 n\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia hay kh\u00f4ng. M\u1ed9t HLV tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft ch\u1eebng 10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed7i n\u0103m. \u1ede c\u1ea5p CLB, con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 60. \u0110\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i th\u00ec lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, v\u1eady n\u00ean th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t qu\u00e3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\na\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-vuot-mat-arsenal-vu-tien-ve-nzonzi-180-191340.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-phat-bieu-ve-ozil-172-191156.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Arsenal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00fap Ozil t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1354","checkdouble":"191436"},{"date":"15:48 17/07","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/courtois-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</h2><br>\r\n<h2>1. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 10 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9. Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh, m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang theo 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i 23. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD 17 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV Miura khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p mang theo 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t bao g\u1ed3m 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, 7 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, 7 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n h\u1ebft t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd sang Indonesia c\u00f9ng HLV Park Hang Seo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n cho m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng va ch\u1ea1m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/24/Thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-du-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i \u0111i 10 c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. HAGL v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb hai CLB c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u1ea5t V-League hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 g\u1ed3m \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Duy M\u1ea1nh, Th\u00e0nh Chung v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 l\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 6 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh, H\u1ed3ng Duy, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 V\u0103n S\u01a1n v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng. V\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed9 khung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0y. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u1ea3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1eabn HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc Huy va Xuan Truong da cap tai U23 Viet Nam\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. V\u00e0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i v\u00e0 L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i sinh ng\u00e0y 26/5/1995. Anh cao 1m76, n\u1eb7ng 69kg v\u00e0 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 15 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trinh Van Loi\" title=\"Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/hi-phong-clb-tphcm-vong-21-vleague-2017_1w6rybg36rtj01fp39bd780xmb.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u1edbp n\u0103ng khi\u1ebfu HAGL v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n L\u1ea1ch Tray theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 cao 1m65 nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, Th\u00e0nh Long c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng. Anh ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea3 V\u0103n L\u1ee3i v\u00e0 Th\u00e0nh Long \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong s\u1ed1 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u binh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd l\u00fac n\u00e0y HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 g\u1ecdi \u0111\u00fang 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 V\u0103n L\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 t\u1ea1i Nga c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh 18 tr\u1eadn/19 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 7 tr\u00ean BXH. V\u00ec th\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Nguyen Anh Duc ghi ban vao luoi Jordan\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Jordan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/nguyen-anh-duc-hay-cu-phieu-khi-doi-chan-con-cho-phep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Anh \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 su\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn \u2018kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t\u2019 gi\u1eefa Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 trung phong h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4n ngoan, kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c c\u00f2n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1 ho\u1eb7c 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng (S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (FLC Thanh H\u00f3a), \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh (Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC), Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (SLNA), Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung, \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh, L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n, Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy (HAGL), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i (Viettel), Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (HAGL), L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng), Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c (SLNA)\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (HAGL), Ho\u00e0ng Minh Tu\u1ea5n (Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh), H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng), Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh (B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng).\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\">Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh: M\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</span><br>\r\n\u0110i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bai-toan-hau-u23-viet-nam-lam-sao-de-giu-lua-toi-asiad-168-179252.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/25/bai-toan-hau-u23-viet-nam-lam-sao-de-giu-lua-toi-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bai-toan-hau-u23-viet-nam-lam-sao-de-giu-lua-toi-asiad-168-179252.html\">B\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u1eadu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: L\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef l\u1eeda t\u1edbi Asiad?</span><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a qua, th\u00ec li\u1ec7u nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd l\u00e0m g\u00ec...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1353","checkdouble":"191438"},{"date":"16:44 17/07","title":"Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea9u, Hart \u201cmu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t\u201d sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/17/joe-hart-sang-my-du-dau-cung-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Joe Hart sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Daily Mail g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1edfi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hart ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Man City</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man City, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea1t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart ra kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. Anh b\u1ecb \u0111em cho Torino v\u00e0 West Ham m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Hart t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHart th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i West Ham trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a. C\u1ea3 Torino v\u00e0 West Ham \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 31 tu\u1ed5i. Anh bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City nh\u01b0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u00e1nh m\u1eaft t\u1edbi b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Joe Hart sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/4/19/Joe-Hart-sang-My-du-dau-cung-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hart th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Torino v\u00e0 West Ham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Hart v\u1edbi Man xanh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Guardiola tin d\u00f9ng. C\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Shrewsbury Town nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/ n\u0103m v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Joe Hart ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm r\u1eddi Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. V\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Citizens tham d\u1ef1 International Champions Cup t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. \u0110\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Hart m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Man City sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart sap roi Man City lan nua.\" title=\"Joe Hart s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/17/joe-hart-sang-my-du-dau-cung-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Hart sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111i v\u1edbi Joe Hart sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Phil Foden. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb 18 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Anh d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ebfn Chicago cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Foden \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111i M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi Man City m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Jorginho. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea c\u00f9ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Maurizio Sarri. Man City c\u0169ng c\u00f3 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Mateo Kovacic song kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic-180-191234.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/Man-City-tu-choi-dua-Mateo-Kovacic-roi-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic-180-191234.html\">Real Madrid h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Mateo Kovacic</span><br>\r\n<span>Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vua-sang-man-city-bom-tan-mahrez-da-no-tung-troi-421-191068.html\">V\u1eeba sang Man City, bom t\u1ea5n Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 \u201cn\u1ed5\u201d tung tr\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao-172-191050.html\">\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\">Man City CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/toi-luot-man-city-vao-cuoc-vu-hang-hot-world-cup-2018-172-190594.html\">T\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Man City v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-man-city-172-190593.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1352","checkdouble":"191439"},{"date":"15:47 17/07","title":"Nghi v\u1ea5n: Huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/giac-mong-word-cup-cua-bong-da-viet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1 chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp khi\u1ebfn d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng tranh c\u00e3i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nHCV c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp?!<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i 90 ph\u00fat v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 4-2 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, l\u1ec5 trao gi\u1ea3i cho nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u00e0n trao gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng cho nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ec7n tay &ldquo;th\u00f3&rdquo; m\u1ea5t 1 chi\u1ebfc trong l\u1ec5 trao gi\u1ea3i. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecdt qua nh\u1eefng \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh m\u00e1y quay, d\u00f9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh chi\u1ebfc ruy b\u0103ng m\u00e0u xanh c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m g\u1ecdn trong t\u00fai c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef n\u00e0y. H\u00e0nh vi k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean di\u1ec5n ra ngay c\u1ea1nh T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Nga Putin, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t t\u00e1n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1 chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp \u1edf l\u1ec5 trao gi\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"1 chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp \u1edf l\u1ec5 trao gi\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/giac-mong-word-cup-cua-bong-da-viet.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>1 chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTr\u00ean Twitter, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean, v\u00ec sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef n\u00e0y d\u00e1m \u0103n c\u1eafp m\u1ed9t v\u1eadt quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady trong l\u1ec5 trao gi\u1ea3i, ngay b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Putin. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn m\u1ec9a mai cho r\u1eb1ng, b\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb ng\u1ea5m m\u01b0a n\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u00e9t v\u00e0o t\u00fai.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c \u00e1c \u00fd h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef n\u00e0y gi\u1ea5u chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em t\u1eb7ng&hellip; Lionel Messi, ho\u1eb7c Harry Kane c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u00f2n cho r\u1eb1ng, b\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y cho&hellip; n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 t\u1ed9i, b\u1edfi 23 chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao t\u1eb7ng cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Trong \u0111\u00f3, chi\u1ebfc huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp tr\u00ean, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf v\u00e0o t\u00fai \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef an to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1edd n\u00e0y qua \u0111o\u1ea1n clip b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/17/hcv.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018-188-191415.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018-188-191415.html\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Paul Pogba lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef trong tay t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n, n\u01a1i in h\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 y\u00eau d\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh qua \u0111\u1eddi c\u00e1ch...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/chan-dung-nu-tong-thong-ham-mo-bong-da-cua-croatia-188-191355.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/chan-dung-nu-tong-thong-ham-mo-bong-da-cua-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/chan-dung-nu-tong-thong-ham-mo-bong-da-cua-croatia-188-191355.html\">Ch\u00e2n dung n\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Croatia</span><br>\r\nN\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1351","checkdouble":"191442"},{"date":"16:21 17/07","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</h2><br>\r\n<h2>1. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 10 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9. Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh, m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang theo 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i 23. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD 17 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV Miura khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p mang theo 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t bao g\u1ed3m 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, 7 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, 7 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n h\u1ebft t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd sang Indonesia c\u00f9ng HLV Park Hang Seo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n cho m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng va ch\u1ea1m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/24/Thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-du-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i \u0111i 10 c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. HAGL v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb hai CLB c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u1ea5t V-League hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 g\u1ed3m \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Duy M\u1ea1nh, Th\u00e0nh Chung v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 l\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 6 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh, H\u1ed3ng Duy, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 V\u0103n S\u01a1n v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng. V\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed9 khung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0y. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u1ea3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1eabn HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc Huy va Xuan Truong da cap tai U23 Viet Nam\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. V\u00e0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i v\u00e0 L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i sinh ng\u00e0y 26/5/1995. Anh cao 1m76, n\u1eb7ng 69kg v\u00e0 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 15 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trinh Van Loi\" title=\"Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/hi-phong-clb-tphcm-vong-21-vleague-2017_1w6rybg36rtj01fp39bd780xmb.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u1edbp n\u0103ng khi\u1ebfu HAGL v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n L\u1ea1ch Tray theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 cao 1m65 nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, Th\u00e0nh Long c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng. Anh ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea3 V\u0103n L\u1ee3i v\u00e0 Th\u00e0nh Long \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong s\u1ed1 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u binh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd l\u00fac n\u00e0y HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 g\u1ecdi \u0111\u00fang 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 V\u0103n L\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 t\u1ea1i Nga c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh 18 tr\u1eadn/19 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 7 tr\u00ean BXH. V\u00ec th\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Nguyen Anh Duc ghi ban vao luoi Jordan\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Jordan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/nguyen-anh-duc-hay-cu-phieu-khi-doi-chan-con-cho-phep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Anh \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 su\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn \u2018kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t\u2019 gi\u1eefa Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 trung phong h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4n ngoan, kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c c\u00f2n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1 ho\u1eb7c 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng (S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (FLC Thanh H\u00f3a), \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh (Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC), Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (SLNA), Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung, \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh, L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n, Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy (HAGL), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i (Viettel), Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (HAGL), L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng), Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c (SLNA)\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (HAGL), Ho\u00e0ng Minh Tu\u1ea5n (Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh), H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng), Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh (B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng).\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\">Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh: M\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</span><br>\r\n\u0110i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bai-toan-hau-u23-viet-nam-lam-sao-de-giu-lua-toi-asiad-168-179252.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/25/bai-toan-hau-u23-viet-nam-lam-sao-de-giu-lua-toi-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bai-toan-hau-u23-viet-nam-lam-sao-de-giu-lua-toi-asiad-168-179252.html\">B\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u1eadu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: L\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef l\u1eeda t\u1edbi Asiad?</span><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a qua, th\u00ec li\u1ec7u nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd l\u00e0m g\u00ec...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1350","checkdouble":"191444"},{"date":"16:25 17/07","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-xherdan-shaqiri-cap-ben-liverpool.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13.7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Xherdan Shaqiri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nXherdan Shaqiri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0 anh mong \u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, khi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 r\u1eddi Bayern Munich anh c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb The Kop \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a&nbsp;m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri Ai vui ai bu\u1ed3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri Ai vui ai bu\u1ed3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Liverpool-mua-thanh-cong-Xherdan-Shaqiri-Ai-vui-ai-buon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Shaqiri h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 3 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Stoke City, Xherdan Shaqiri \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110 Liverpool v\u00e0 HLV Klopp. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 13.7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 t\u1eeb Stoke City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb nh\u1ecf, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c gi\u00fap Liverpool gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m 3 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Shaqiri s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Stoke City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Stoke kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u01afu ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 l\u00e0 gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng, song h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Stoke khong the giu chan Shaqiri\" title=\"Stoke kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Shaqiri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/stoke.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Stoke kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Shaqiri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Shaqiri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Stoke City. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ghi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 43% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Stoke \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nShaqiri l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Stoke, anh chi\u1ebfm 50% s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Shaqiri ra \u0111i, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Stoke s\u1ebd b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Shaqiri, Swansea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Lukasz Fabianski v\u00e0o tay West Ham, trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Bet365, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: HLV Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 - Vladimir Petkovic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Xherdan Shaqiri l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9. 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u1edf Euro 2016 v\u00e0 World Cup 2018 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Vladimir Petkovic rat mung khi Shaqiri cap ben Liverpool\" title=\"HLV Vladimir Petkovic r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng khi Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/161852-hlv.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Vladimir Petkovic r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng khi Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong c\u1ea3 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn n\u00e0y Shaqiri \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool, anh h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t, Shaqiri s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. Ngo\u00e0i ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Liverpool c\u0169ng gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i&nbsp;thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Vladimir Petkovic c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool, b\u1edfi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o The Kop kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Shaqiri s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi. Khi \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t, Shaqiri s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Mane, Firmino v\u00e0 Salah. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c The Kop ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Co hoi ra san cua Solanke o mua giai toi giam di dang ke\" title=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Solanke \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/solonke.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Solanke \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Shaqiri, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb b\u00ean ph\u00eda Liverpool s\u1ebd b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu Dominic Solanke, Rhian Brewster v\u00e0 Ben Woodburn kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ee9c \u00e9p gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u bu\u1ed9c Klopp ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n.&nbsp;Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Shaqiri, nh\u1eefng Solanke, Brewster v\u00e0 Woodburn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u&nbsp;h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Mohamed Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Philippe Coutinho r\u1eddi Liverpool c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, Mohammed Salah tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah\" title=\"Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/HLV-Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Salah-va-viec-gia-han-hop-dong--hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng khi Liverpool mua Shaqiri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, anh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng&nbsp;Anh v\u00e0 Champions League b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quan tr\u1ecdng, Klopp kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m \u0111\u1ec3 Salah ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn Salah d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2018 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a t\u1edbi, g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng d\u00e0nh cho Salah s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt khi Shaqiri c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Anfield. HLV Klopp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Shaqiri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Salah trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Shaqiri, Salah s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Moses Simon</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Moses Simon l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho KAA Gent \u1edf B\u1ec9. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Shaqiri, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Moses Simon khong con co hoi toi Liverpool\" title=\"Moses Simon kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/simnon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Moses Simon kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n3 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o KAA Gent, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ghi 21 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 108 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Liverpool, HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Moses Simon kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1349","checkdouble":"191445"},{"date":"17:39 17/07","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/alex-sandro-dong-y-sang-psg-thay-vi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alex Sandro \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sang PSG thay v\u00ec M.U. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo s\u00e1t sao h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Juventus su\u1ed1t 1 n\u0103m qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alex Sandro</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlex Sandro n\u1ed5i l\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Porto v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus. 3 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. \u1ede Sandro s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i luy\u1ec7n trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Alex Sandro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u201cb\u1eaft ch\u1ebft\u201d b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng, t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng d\u1ecdc bi\u00ean tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Sandro \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sang PSG thay v\u00ec MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alex Sandro \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sang PSG thay v\u00ec MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/Alex-Sandro-dong-y-sang-PSG-thay-vi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luke Shaw kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb Mourinho</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111ang r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. HLV Jose Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Ashley Young \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 33 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. M.U c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sandro \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus m\u1edbi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh (112 tri\u1ec7u Euro). Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n \u0111i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t m\u00e0 Alex Sandro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Sandro cua Juventus\" title=\"Alex Sandro cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-177,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng Alex Sandro \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sang PSG thay v\u00ec M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb The Sun, Sandro mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi PSG nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 M.U. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Luke Shaw \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y ch\u1ed7 cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, M.U s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1n Shaw v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 5 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Club America, San Jose Earthquakes, AC Milan, Liverpool v\u00e0 Real Madrid t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n 1 tr\u1eadn n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Bayern Munich t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Leicester r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng 11/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia-172-191421.html\">M.U chi 92 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/psg-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-danny-rose-172-191408.html\">PSG mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Tottenham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ivan-perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-mu-cua-mourinho-172-191400.html\">Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi M.U c\u1ee7a Mourinho?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\">3 l\u00fd do ch\u1ec9 ra M.U c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay sao b\u1ef1 \u0110T Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/99-blind-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-191360.html\">99% c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1348","checkdouble":"191446"},{"date":"17:22 17/07","title":"Sao b\u1ef1 Tottenham c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min c\u00f3\u00a0t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB Tottenham t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 52 tr\u1eadn cho Spurs, v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-min c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD 2018 c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Son Heung-min c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD 2018 c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/liverpool-muon-vuot-mat-mu-va-tottenham-vu-ronaldo-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Son Heung-Min g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2014 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh Huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Son Heung-min h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Spurs tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham gia ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1, \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi nam gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Son Heung-min, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f2n tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n\u2019Jo Hyeon-woo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n s\u1ebd th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m HCV tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng sau. G\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hwang Uijo (Gamba Osaka). <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia v\u00e0 Bahrain.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\nChi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\">VFF c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;line-height:\n115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#222222;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1347","checkdouble":"191451"},{"date":"17:49 17/07","title":"Kante   Jorginho   ???: 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/5-ung-vien-cho-vi-tri-con-lai-noi-hang-tien-ve-chelsea.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-3 trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Napoli. Chelsea mua Jorginho th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Kante l\u00e0 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a The Blues. V\u1eady c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi?\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ai xung dang tien ten vao vi tri con lai noi hang tien ve 3 nguoi cua Chelsea?\" title=\"Ai x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/5-ung-vien-cho-vi-tri-con-lai-noi-hang-tien-ve-chelsea.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ai x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nCesc Fabregas</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,48</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 3,51</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 2</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, HLV Sarri th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-3. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf Stamford Bridge \u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.&nbsp;V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Jorginho</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Kante l\u00e0 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a The Blues.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Jorginho Sarri s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i Chelsea nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Jorginho Sarri s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i Chelsea nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/Chelsea-mua-Jorginho-Sarri-se-thay-doi-Chelsea-nhu-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cesc Fabregas \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Jorginho \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u1eb1m cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa khi c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng. Cesc Fabregas ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea. F4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV Maurizio Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 3,51 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i/90 ph\u00fat, anh c\u0169ng ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi 1,48 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u00fat xa t\u1ed1t, F4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Fabregas t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng kh\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, m\u00f9a t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 tinh t\u00fay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ross Barkley</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,37</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,37</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoss Barkley chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay t\u1eeb Everton v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo&nbsp;khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u cho The Blues.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ross Barkley co man ra mat khong thanh cong\" title=\"Ross Barkley c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/25/conte-noi-gi-ve-su-mo-nhat-cua-ross-barkley.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ross Barkley c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 131 ph\u00fat \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ef1u sao Everton kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Barkley \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111ang kh\u00e1t khao ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, Barkley ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 HLV Sarri d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barkley t\u1ea1i Everton (2015/16) anh ghi t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 8 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Goodison Park ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i ghi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu 8 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoss Barkley s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, Barkley ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Ruben Loftus-Cheek</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,54</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,25</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 2</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ruben Loftus-Cheek. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" title=\"tien ve Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/10/sao-tre-chelsea-toi-crystal-palace-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ruben Loftus-Cheek nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLoftus-Cheek th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n, tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Loftus-Cheek kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao, nh\u01b0ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, HLV 58 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m Loftus-Cheek \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Aleksandr Golovin</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 2,2</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,6</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 5</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleksandr Golovin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><br>\r\n            <img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Golovin\" title=\"Alex Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/chelsea-gap-doi-thu-o-thuong-vu-golovin.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA, anh \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Nga, \u00f4ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Golovin v\u1ec1 The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA v\u00e0 \u0110T Nga, Golovin th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ch\u01a1i sau ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, song v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u00f3 trung b\u00ecnh 1,9 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra 1,6 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i/90 ph\u00fat, anh c\u00f3 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 2,9</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,6</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 11</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Theo Corriere dello Sport, Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/16/Chelsea-muon-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-cua-Lazio-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u00e3 ghi 12 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A, anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh 2,9 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi Hamsik (3,2), ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Napoli \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 Lazio \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1346","checkdouble":"191452"},{"date":"09:57 17/07","title":"Real Madrid c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/real-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-ve-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai, t\u1edd The Telegraph tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Los Blancos.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Zidane c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u1edf Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/HLV-Lopetegui-quyet-khong-de-Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-Madrid--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Gareth Bale&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Vi\u1ec7c Bale tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gareth Bale, Mourinho \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i MU th\u00ec Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Bale r\u1eddi Real l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai, t\u1edd The Telegraph tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Los Blancos.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" title=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/real-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-ve-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Gareth Bale \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Lopetegui</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-180-191238.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bale c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Lopetegui</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Bale, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Real v\u1eeba m\u1ea5t Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u1eefa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, HLV Lopetegui c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Eden Hazard \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1345","checkdouble":"191416"},{"date":"10:19 17/07","title":"HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-tri-gia-50-trieu-bang-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jorginho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n mang v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Napoli t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Maurizio-Sarri-phat-bieu-ve-Jorginho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jorginho</span>. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London, \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Napoli nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ph\u1ea3i chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Chelsea, Jorginho s\u1ebd \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 5. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft, Jorginho chia s\u1ebb: \u201cChelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf Anh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League, b\u1edfi v\u1eady khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Chelsea c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Jorginho</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri giup Chelsea mua Jorginho\" title=\"Sarri gi\u00fap Chelsea mua Jorginho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-tri-gia-50-trieu-bang-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cJorginho kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf Napoli, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi Jorginho, b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ri\u00eang\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n hi\u1ec3u h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n g\u00ec v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho CLB\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1344","checkdouble":"191417"},{"date":"10:49 17/07","title":"Chelsea chi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c BL\u0110 M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U chi g\u1ea7n 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Ivan Perisic, c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u1ecd t\u1eebng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, khi anh g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao Croatia c\u0169ng ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u, Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Perisic v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp theo, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ante Rebic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Rebic \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Eintracht Frankfurt \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Arsenal c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Rebic v\u00e0 Rakitic\" title=\"Rebic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Rebic v\u00e0 Rakitic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa, bao g\u1ed3m 1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p chia tay Anthony Martial, M.U s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Wilian, Gareth Bale &ndash; v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Ivan Perisic c\u00f9ng Ante Rebic.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Keita, Shaqiri; Man City c\u00f3 Riyad Mahrez; Arsenal s\u1edf h\u1eefu 5 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Chelsea c\u0169ng k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Jorginho. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0y d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/DT-Phap-tao-dang-cung-cup-vang-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba</span><br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i b\u00e1o tr\u00ean The Sun, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-1707-172-191425.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/12/tong-hop-nhung-sieu-pham-ban-thang-cua-ronaldo-khi-con-o-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-1707-172-191425.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 17/07</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i \u1edf, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 17/07.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1343","checkdouble":"191418"},{"date":"11:00 17/07","title":"Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/DT-Phap-tao-dang-cung-cup-vang-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i b\u00e1o tr\u00ean The Sun, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.\r\n</h2><h2><br />\r\nPogba n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0i b\u00e1o n\u00e0y ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u1eeba qua, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbp gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 Hugo Lloris \u0111ang n\u1eafm chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, nh\u01b0ng Pogba v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Les Bleus.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i vinh danh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ee9ng ra ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eeda tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p. V\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a M.U l\u00e0 Michael Carrick gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n David De Gea hay Nemanja Matic ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Paul Pogba ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edbt m\u00e0u m\u00e8 v\u00e0 t\u00f4 v\u1ebd h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, anh ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf h\u01a1n, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tham gia nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt khi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tung ra \u0111\u00fang 2 c\u00fa s\u00fat trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ham &ldquo;s\u00fat b\u1eady&rdquo; trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man United.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 th\u1ebf quen thu\u1ed9c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/DT-Phap-tao-dang-cung-cup-vang-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br />\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 Rami chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n r\u1eb1ng, Pogba \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau, nh\u01b0ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ecf h\u00e1ng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed5 h\u00f4i, x\u1eafn tay \u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p &ndash; Hugo Lloris c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng, Pogba \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u00ean suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd k\u00edch th\u00edch tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng gi\u1eefa 2 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018-188-191415.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018-188-191415.html\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br />\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Paul Pogba lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef trong tay t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n, n\u01a1i in h\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 y\u00eau d\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh qua \u0111\u1eddi c\u00e1ch...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc-421-191349.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc-421-191349.html\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba, cho ph\u00e9p... \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c</span><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng Rio Ferdinand, Paul Scholes hay kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Roy Keane cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1edf m\u00e0y n\u1edf m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf sau khi c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-len-ngoi-vo-dich-pogba-va-man-trinh-dien-dap-tan-moi-chi-trich-421-191329.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/pogba-duoc-huyen-thoai-khen-ngoi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-len-ngoi-vo-dich-pogba-va-man-trinh-dien-dap-tan-moi-chi-trich-421-191329.html\">Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch: Paul Pogba v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1eadp tan m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span><br />\r\n0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng Pogba trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1342","checkdouble":"191419"},{"date":"10:40 17/07","title":"C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1eebng gi\u00fap Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/20/cong-than-tung-giup-quang-nam-vo-dich-bi-thanh-ly-hop-dong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Claudecir Junior do g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</h2><h2>CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/CLB-Quang-Nam-thanh-ly-hop-dong-voi-Claudecir-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Claudecir Junior l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1ea1i V-League 2017, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Claudecir \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i do ch\u1ecbu \u00e1n k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt t\u1eeb CLB, Claudecir \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Qu\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 10 V-League, Claudecir c\u00f2n d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng sau pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 TP.HCM, Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00ecnh Lu\u1eadt. Theo k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129, Claudecir b\u1ecb g\u00e3y x\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e1c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ea3ng Nam g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i binh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u2018\u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ai n\u1ea5y \u0111i\u2019. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00ednh Claudecir mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia tay \u2018c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n\u2019 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung t\u00e2n binh Warley Oliveira thay th\u1ebf. Ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eeba gia nh\u1eadp Qu\u1ea3ng Nam n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Brazil. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Oliveira t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi sang ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u1edf\u00a0Kuwait m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft\u00a0cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Claudecir, m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 sao nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n Trung \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng (Suleiman). Thay th\u1ebf anh l\u00e0 Thiago, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9c<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai su\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i binh l\u00e0 Douglas, Warley Oliveira c\u00f9ng su\u1ea5t nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9c (Thiago). Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 9 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng khi k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 19 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\">SLNA 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam (KT): Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng v\u00e0 Olaha, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-quang-nam-44-binh-duong-vong-18-vleague-2018-325-190702.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/tong-hop-quang-nam-44-binh-duong-vong-18-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-quang-nam-44-binh-duong-vong-18-vleague-2018-325-190702.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 4-4 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (V\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nHai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0110inh Thanh Trung c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1341","checkdouble":"191420"}]}